title: MakerBot lays off another twenty percent of its workers
text:
MakerBot lays off another twenty percent of its workers 
Published By: Tuaw.com - Today 
In April MakerBot laid off 20 percent of its workforce. Roughly six months later, its doing it again, trimming another fifth of its payroll ...
